{"tid":2463424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（死得轟烈）見光死？ H&M中国官網把維尼系列下架了","createTime":"2021-03-26T16:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T02:58:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8bbbe3f02b049dee4754a11d712bf9e21a3dc7f6","tid":2463424,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:22:57.000Z","msg":"國際知名品牌H&amp;M發出拒用中國新疆棉花的聲明後，中國網民開始發起獵巫行動，H&amp;M於淘寶及天貓等平台的官方皆被下架，台港藝人也急發聲明切割。然而有眼尖網友在今天下午發現，H&amp;M官網仍推出迪士尼「小熊維尼」新品，引起網友熱議，但或許是見光死，目前中國官方網站疑已經將其下架。<br />\n<br />\n本報下午報導指出，H&amp;M中國官網仍可以搜尋到「小熊維尼」童裝新品，但是服飾原料僅標示為「棉」，而非中國人所支持的「新疆棉」。<br />\n<br />\n消息一出讓網友戲稱「反正都要死了，倒不如轟轟烈烈」，網友也回應「H&amp;M新代言人」，笑稱「棉花什麼的只是藉口，這才是根本原因」、「抓到了！H&amp;M跟中國撕破臉的真正原因！」<br />\n<br />\n然而不到1天，就在今晚，H&amp;M中國官網悄悄地把小熊維尼合作系列下架。截稿前，甚至進不去H&amp;M中國官網。<br />\n<br />\n2013年6月時中國主席習近平訪問美國，與時任總統歐巴馬會面時被拍到一張照片，中國網友將兩人的身形比作迪士尼動畫片中的角色「小熊維尼」與「跳跳虎」，然而看似中國網友的玩笑，卻被中國當局禁止討論，甚至被中國社群平台微博列為禁用詞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3480418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3480418&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=e472edee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3480418&h=04135742\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3480418</a>"},{"pid":"51d235ae377c20758d78286a803e06ff9c7f4a94","tid":2463424,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"其實中共官方已經承認咗習近平 = 小熊維尼？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04170949/image1533373585520.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F04170949%2Fimage1533373585520.png&h=512f2591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180804/s00004/2f1b1dc3e41b348414bf5c8639409b74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180804%2Fs00004%2F2f1b1dc3e41b348414bf5c8639409b74.jpg&h=8cfdf1d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dfd413a66e6d3d7bd7e8b0e3ee9ca6ccbef5bf5","tid":2463424,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04919ac41a2b53d392f939fd4637b245f4f71d8","tid":2463424,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T18:17:39.000Z","msg":"然後show跳跳虎 豬仔 同個黑影囉"},{"pid":"c4f0be6c62d8c9e4c4764af3ef5bce14e97012b3","tid":2463424,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af1578545c9e0f065b741edb3cd15cf041e2e5b","tid":2463424,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:58:25.000Z","msg":"中國真強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}